donor_name: OFFICE OF THE HIGH COMMISSIONER FOR HUMA
outputs.output_descr: The first phase of the JSP was launched in 2003. In 2005 the project was revised and a new phase began and ended in 2008. The current JSP is the result of the second revision and focuses on the achievement of the following 6 strategic outcomes: 1) Enhancement of skills and competencies of justice sector actors; 2) Support the justice decentralization process; 3) Strengthen the Prosecution Services; 4) Strengthen capacity of the corrections services to uphold public safety; 5) Enhance access to justice for all; 6) establish the CEO of the Programme

project_descr: Enhancing the Democratic Rule of Law through Strengthening the Justice System in Timor-Leste (Revised Justice System Programme)
